5|$|In March 2016, Wicked surpassed $1 {{billion in}} total Broadway revenue, joining both The Phantom of <b>the</b> <b>Opera</b> and The Lion King {{as the only}} Broadway shows to do so. In July 2017, Wicked surpassed The Phantom of <b>the</b> <b>Opera</b> as Broadway's second-highest-grossing show, {{trailing}} only The Lion King.|$|E
